entries.femaleVariant: Hurghh... Last round, k-kay?
Gettin' all them diverse states to unite without a federal government? Forget it.
That what you ass-kissin' minions at Militech chant all day long?
Awright, I'm sold. Nearest karaoke – now!
Last round? Not somethin' I ever have. I drink clear through the night and come mornin', I grab another stiff one. Or two, if you know what I mean, heheh.
You have a-any idea what she's talking about?
She's basically sayin' she's had enough, that's what.
Pshh, enough? Never. You haven't seen nothin' yet.
You just don't hold your booze well, that's all. Civilization was founded on this sweet nectar! Eons of tradition, culture, philosophy…
Got a PhD in drinkin', now? If I feel like shit, I down a bottle. Ain't nothing more to it.
Who's comin' with me?
Ugh, I'd rather spend the next hour dry heaving over a shitter.
Count me in. The karaoke, not the dry heaving…
Want a strong federation? Gonna need a strong-ass leader to steer the ship. Know what I'm sayin'?
The fuck're you talking about? A federation? Not happening.
I'm talkin' about liberty, man. Freedom!
Want my two cents on freedom? Sure as shit don't have it when you're dumped in the "free" market with nothin' but your dick in your hand.
Texas? The fuck're YOU talkin' about now?
Whaddaya think? Full-blown state autonomy!
Fuck me... If I'd known I was drinkin' with a radical devolutionit. Man...
No fascist, federalist scuzzbucket from Texas or wherever's gonna tell me how to live my life.
Y'all preachin' autonomy, but you're nothin' but a corpo sheep.
You... Fuck you...!
Recommend anything?
